<Layout title="Returns & refunds — saasuluk" description="saasuluk returns & refunds — 30-day returns on physical goods, instant refunds on digital orders, and how to start a return.">
  <h1>Returns &amp; refunds</h1>
  <p class="tag">A starter policy — replace it with your real terms before launch. It is not legal advice.</p>
  <h2>Digital products &amp; licenses</h2>
  <p>Because digital goods (downloads, licenses, source access) are delivered instantly and can't be returned, sales are final once access is granted. If something is broken or not as described, email us within <b>14 days</b> and we'll make it right — a fix, a replacement, or a refund.</p>
  <h2>Physical goods</h2>
  <p>Physical items (like the Founder Tee) can be returned within <b>30 days</b> of delivery for a full refund, provided they're unworn, unwashed, and in original condition. Start a return from <a href="/dashboard/s/orders">your orders</a> or by replying to your order confirmation email.</p>
  <h2>How refunds work</h2>
  <p>Approved refunds go back to your original payment method via Stripe, typically within 5–10 business days. We'll email you when the refund is issued. Original shipping is non-refundable unless the return is due to our error.</p>
  <h2>Damaged or wrong items</h2>
  <p>If your order arrives damaged or incorrect, contact us within <b>7 days</b> with a photo and your order number — we'll send a replacement or refund at no cost, including return shipping.</p>
  <p style="margin-top:24px">Questions? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> — we read every message.</p>
</Layout>
